# Version Strategy

## Overview

This project uses SemVer (MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH) with a multi-branch strategy:
- **master**: Framework version (general capabilities)
- **Feature branches**: Feature completion version (may differ from master)

## Version Locations

Always update together:
- `interface/package.json` → `"version"`
- `src/version.h` → `VERSION_MAJOR`, `VERSION_MINOR`, `VERSION_PATCH`, `VERSION_STRING`
- `CHANGELOG.md` → Document changes under `[version]` heading

## Bumping Rules

### Master Branch

- **PATCH**: Doc fixes, rule updates, dependency patches
- **MINOR**: General improvements merged from features (new patterns, docs, capabilities)
- **MAJOR**: Breaking framework changes (API redesign, architecture overhaul)

### Feature Branches (serial, display, led, etc.)

- **PATCH**: Bug fixes, refinements
- **MINOR**: Feature milestones (e.g., first working prototype, new capability)
- **MAJOR**: Breaking changes within that feature

## Current Versions (as of Feb 2026)

- **master**: 0.6.1 → 0.7.0 after merging serial general docs
- **serial**: 0.6.1 (synced with master after merge)
- **display**: TBD (start from master version when branched)

## Workflow

1. Feature branch reaches milestone → bump feature branch version
2. Feature branch has general improvements → merge to master → bump master version
3. Feature branch syncs from master: `git merge master` (optional, keeps in sync)

## Commands

```powershell
# Bump version (updates package.json, version.h, creates git tag)
cd interface
npm version patch|minor|major

# Update CHANGELOG.md and src/version.h manually
git add CHANGELOG.md src/version.h
git commit --amend --no-edit
git push
git push --tags
```

## Example: Master 0.6.1 → 0.7.0

```powershell
# On master after merging general docs from serial
cd interface
npm version minor  # 0.6.1 → 0.7.0

# Update version.h
# #define VERSION_MAJOR 0
# #define VERSION_MINOR 7  # was 6
# #define VERSION_PATCH 0  # was 1
# #define VERSION_STRING "0.7.0"

# Update CHANGELOG.md
# ## [0.7.0] - 2026-02-17
# ### Added
# - Merged general docs/rules from serial branch
# - OTA upload documentation and rules
# - Hardware pin configuration docs
# - Multi-protocol weight forwarder patterns
# - Diagnostics example for UART testing

git add CHANGELOG.md src/version.h
git commit --amend --no-edit
git push
git push --tags
```

